name: Araneaframework
body:
### Araneaframework

### Status
The main purpose of this site is to make Araneaframework documentation available for the world. This documentation was previously located at araneaframework.org.

Although the framework has been used in several projects it does no longer have official support. It is hosted under Nortal account but there is no dedicated person to handle the bugs or improvement ideas posted as issues. 

### Binaries
Uploaded to Bintray: bintray.com/nortal/araneaframework

### Documentation
